name: Check for Duplicate Users
fullName: Platform Admin Management: Check for Duplicate Users

steps.name: Given I log in to the TNA application as an admin and click on the "Create New User" button
When I input the details of an already existing platform admin and click on the save button
Then I should see an error message stating "User already exists"
